Title: Create commands to say to smart homes
Description: Create a command that you would say to tell a smart home whether the lights should be on or off.
Keywords: text, creative, research, academic, writing, smart home, internet of things, artificial intelligence
Answer.WritingTexts: At 7 am please turn the lights on low.|After 9 pm please turn the porch light off.|When it gets dark out side please turn the porch lights on.|When I go to step into a room please turn the lights on.|After 10 p.m. if I am not going to be home please turn the living room light on.
